Package com.datasift.dropwizard.kafka.consumer

Interface Summary
KafkaConsumer Interface for consuming a stream of messages from Kafka.
StreamProcessor<T> Processes an Iterable of messages of type T.
 

Class Summary
KafkaConsumerHealthCheck A HealthCheck to monitor the health of a KafkaConsumer.
MessageProcessor<T> Processes messages of type T from a Kafka message stream.
SynchronousConsumer<T> A KafkaConsumer that processes messages synchronously using an ExecutorService.
